msgstr "Predvaja uvodni video, ko zažene Kodi"

msgctxt "#31232"
msgid "Clear current intro video file and back to default"
msgstr "Počisti trenutno uvodno video datoteko in nazaj na privzeto"

msgctxt "#31233"
msgid "Clear the intro video file selected by the user and back to Aeon Tajo's default."
msgstr "Počistite uvodno video datoteko, ki jo je izbral uporabnik, in se vrnite na privzeto Aeon Tajo."

msgctxt "#31234"
msgid "Adds a layer that simulates falling snow on all Kodi screens, with four available intensity levels."
msgstr "Doda plast, ki simulira padajoči sneg na vseh zaslonih Kodi, s štirimi razpoložljivimi stopnjami intenzivnosti."

msgctxt "#31235"
