msgctxt "#31290"
msgid "Thanks for using Aeon Tajo—I really hope you’re enjoying it. Creating and maintaining a Kodi skin like this takes hundreds of hours of work. If Aeon Tajo is something you enjoy and find useful, supporting it helps me keep working on it and ensures it can continue evolving in the future. [CR][CR]If you decide to do so, you’ll receive frequent updates with new features and bug fixes, along with videos, media packs, and easy-to-follow articles with detailed tips to help you get the most out of everything Aeon Tajo has to offer, together with my sincere gratitude for your support. [CR][CR]For more information, visit [B][COLOR=themecolor]patreon.com[/B][/COLOR] and search for the creator [COLOR=themecolor][B]Aeon Tajo[/B][/COLOR], or go to [COLOR=themecolor][B]patreon.com/aeontajo[/B][/COLOR].[CR][CR]Thanks!"
msgstr "Hvala, ker uporabljate Aeon Tajo — resnično upam, da vam je všeč! Ustvarjanje in vzdrževanje skina Kodi, kot je ta, zahteva stotine ur dela. Če vam Aeon Tajo prinaša užitek in je koristen, mi vaša podpora pomaga nadaljevati z delom na njem in zagotavlja, da se bo v prihodnosti še naprej razvijal. [CR][CR]Če se odločite za to, boste prejemali pogosta posodobitve z novimi funkcijami in popravki napak, skupaj z videoposnetki, medijskimi paketi in podrobnimi članki z nasveti, ki vam bodo pomagali kar najbolje izkoristiti vse, kar ponuja Aeon Tajo, skupaj z mojo iskreno hvaležnostjo za vašo podporo. [CR][CR]Za več informacij obiščite [B][COLOR=themecolor]patreon.com[/B][/COLOR] in poiščite ustvarjalca [COLOR=themecolor][B]Aeon Tajo[/B][/COLOR] ali pojdite na [COLOR=themecolor][B]patreon.com/aeontajo[/B][/COLOR].[CR][CR]Hvala!"

