msgstr "Ne vsili pogledov"

msgctxt "#31419"
msgid "Forced view"
msgstr "Vsiljen pogled"

msgctxt "#31420"
msgid "Enable or disable views"
msgstr "Omogoči ali onemogoči poglede"

msgctxt "#31422"
msgid "No embedded subs"
msgstr "Brez vgrajenih podnapisov"

msgctxt "#31423"
msgid "Auto-open audio/subtitle selector at video start"
msgstr "Samodejno odpri izbirnik zvoka/podnapisov ob zagonu videa"

msgctxt "#31424"
msgid "Automatically opens an audio and subtitle selector when starting playback of movies and episodes, allowing you to see which tracks are active and change them directly before continuing."
msgstr "Samodejno odpre izbirnik zvoka in podnapisov ob zagonu predvajanja filmov in epizod, kar omogoča vpogled v aktivne sledi in njihovo neposredno spremembo pred nadaljevanjem."

msgctxt "#31425"
msgid "Search music video links for songs not in your library"
msgstr "Poišči video povezave za skladbe, ki niso v vaši knjižnici"

msgctxt "#31426"
msgid "Similar artists on your library"
msgstr "Podobni izvajalci v vaši knjižnici"

msgctxt "#31435"
msgid "Albums by this artist in your library"
msgstr "Albumi tega izvajalca v vaši knjižnici"

msgctxt "#31436"
msgid "Online info from TheAudioDB.com for music"
msgstr "Spletne informacije iz TheAudioDB.com za glasbo"

msgctxt "#31437"
msgid "Get online information from TheAudioDB.com on the artist and album information screen"
msgstr "Pridobi spletne informacije iz TheAudioDB.com na zaslonu z informacijami o izvajalcu in albumu"

msgctxt "#31438"
msgid "TheAudioDb Helper supplies online data and artwork to display enhanced details for artists and music albums."
msgstr "TheAudioDb Helper zagotavlja spletne podatke in slike za prikaz razširjenih podrobnosti o izvajalcih in glasbenih albumih."

